  <brief_title>Laparoscopic/Robotic-assisted Hysteropexy Versus Vaginal Hysterectomy for the Treatment of Uterovaginal Prolapse</brief_title>
  <acronym>PROLAPSE</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Study of Laparoscopic/Robotic-assisted Hysteropexy Versus Vaginal Hysterectomy for the Treatment of Uterovaginal Prolapse</official_title>
